description: Library to work with NB-Not (Narrow Band Internet of Things) module SIM7020 with built-in support network Protocol MQTT (message queuing telemetry transport). This Library is a tool for working with AT commands and can be easily converted to work with other modules of the SIMCOM family.
name: sim7020

@/example-gsm-check.description: Example to check the network registration.

@/example-publish-to-mqtt.description: Example to publish the pot value to the Adafruit.io web service using the  MQTT Protocol.
